&lt;p&gt;We are looking for an &lt;strong&gt;Atlassian Marketplace Application Support Engineer &lt;/strong&gt;to join our team to partner with cross-functional teams across the company and provide technical and product leadership for our suite of Marketplace Apps.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About You:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
